detaileddescription.para: Only when checkAndLog is set the Method CheckAndLog is active. Default is false. The Method checkAndLog makes a syntax and semantic check of the generated animation commands. The commands are also logged in logFileName from constructor. For semantic check the whole animation environment is build in heap. This consumes a lot of time and heap space. Normally the CheckAndLog Method is switched off.
